Update pidgin-gpg.c

Fixed issue for forwarded chat markers and receipts that were otherwise disabling encryption after every carbonated message sent from Conversations.
(received <message> without <x> always disabled encryption)
Also it might be better from a security perspective to not just fall back to plain text as soon as we receive an unencrypted message-

use "to" instead of "from" for carbonated sent messages to identify the correct communication partner.
